high_descs: Go to the sofa.
Take the knife.
Go to bed.
Move the bread toward you.
Go to the nightstand.
Open the drawer of the nightstand, place the knife at the bottom left of the drawer.
Go to the bed.
Take a slice of bread.
Take a slice of bread. Go to the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the slice of bread on the left side, close the door and preheat the microwave for four seconds. Open the door. Take out the slice of bread. Close the door.
Go to the sidetable.
Place the slice of bread on the sidetable near the wall.
anns.task_desc: Find a pencil, place it in a nightstand drawer. Heat a loaf of Bread in the microwave, place it on the SideTable.

high_descs: Make a left and stand in front of the sofa in the living room.
Pick up the knife from the sofa.
Take the bread to the bedroom.
Walk over to the bread and slice it.
Stand in front of the nightstand drawer.
Open the nightstand drawer and put the knife in it.
Walk over to the bed to where the slice bread is.
Take one piece of slice bread.
Go into the kitchen and stand in front of the microwave.
Open the microwave door to heat up the bread.
Turn around and go back into the bedroom.
Walk to the sidetable and put the bread on top of it.
anns.task_desc: Get the bread and make it hot to put on SideTable.

high_descs: Walk to the sofa on the left.
Pick up the knife on the couch.
Turn around and walk into the bedroom on the left to reach the bed.
Cut the bread on the bed into slices.
Turn left to reach the nightstand.
Put the knife in the top drawer of the nightstand.
Turn around to face the bed.
Pick up a slice of bread from the bed.
Turn around and walk left to exit the room and head to the dining room on the right to reach the microwave on the left.
Heat the slice of bread in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around to exit the room and turn left to enter the bedroom and walk to the sidetable.
Put the slice of bread on top of the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated Bread on the SideTable.
